00:00:11,950 --> 00:00:21,125
<i>Sasameyuki / The Makioka Sisters (1959)</i>

3
00:02:41,536 --> 00:02:46,070
Hello, Sis.

4
00:02:49,688 --> 00:02:51,656
Where's your mom?

5
00:02:52,281 --> 00:02:53,734
She's at home.

6
00:02:54,570 --> 00:02:56,070
I brought a gift

7
00:03:06,641 --> 00:03:07,750
Hello.

8
00:03:09,084 --> 00:03:10,920
Akan-chan, are you going somewhere? Yes

9
00:03:11,139 --> 00:03:14,139
I bought tickets to the concert

10
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,746
My brother is waiting for me at the Osaka office

11
00:03:16,771 --> 00:03:19,094
Do you use that belt?

12
00:03:19,690 --> 00:03:22,336
You also used that belt during the piano concert other day.

13
00:03:22,361 --> 00:03:23,070
Yes.

14
00:03:23,148 --> 00:03:30,031
I was sitting next to you and your belt looked very tight.

15
00:03:30,844 --> 00:03:31,781
Really?

16
00:03:32,664 --> 00:03:34,039
Please turn off the radio

17
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:49,078
Yeah this is bad.

18
00:03:51,328 --> 00:03:51,969
No?

19
00:03:52,359 --> 00:03:53,203
No.

20
00:03:53,547 --> 00:03:55,608
I'll show you my good one.

21
00:03:57,499 --> 00:04:00,163
I want a souvenir

22
00:04:01,656 --> 00:04:05,054
Please stay in this house tonight.

23
00:04:05,583 --> 00:04:08,492
I get it. You have homework

24
00:04:08,883 --> 00:04:09,844
Yes.

25
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:11,804
That's what I thought.

26
00:04:11,829 --> 00:04:14,495
So, just play around and write it properly

27
00:04:14,621 --> 00:04:16,335
I'll show you later.

28
00:04:16,742 --> 00:04:17,617
Try this.

29
00:04:18,891 --> 00:04:19,844
Try this?

30
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,250
Hold on.

31
00:04:30,379 --> 00:04:32,507
This is no good either.

32
00:04:33,273 --> 00:04:36,281
I get it.
This is too new.

33
00:04:36,711 --> 00:04:37,500
Really?

34
00:04:39,906 --> 00:04:40,828
Try this.

35
00:04:51,296 --> 00:04:52,195
Is this ok?

36
00:04:52,474 --> 00:04:54,841
This doesn't feel tight at all

37
00:04:55,071 --> 00:04:58,265
This belt is old and very easy to use.

38
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,554
I see.

39
00:05:00,007 --> 00:05:01,617
You should use your brain a little

40
00:05:01,642 --> 00:05:02,789
Yeah.

41
00:05:03,766 --> 00:05:04,984
It's already this late.

42
00:05:05,506 --> 00:05:08,601
I've already given our workers over to my workplace

43
00:05:08,789 --> 00:05:09,891
I'm not ready.

44
00:05:10,421 --> 00:05:12,495
I will thank you later

45
00:05:13,621 --> 00:05:17,578
Hehe, I know everything, and if you don't have any pocket money, I'll lend it to you

46
00:05:17,876 --> 00:05:19,328
That's a lie.

47
00:05:22,555 --> 00:05:23,891
Kan-chan.

48
00:05:25,253 --> 00:05:28,253
Have you been dating Keibon lately?

49
00:05:29,359 --> 00:05:30,266
Keibon?

50
00:05:31,618 --> 00:05:34,703
Why do you say such things?

51
00:05:38,023 --> 00:05:39,461
Thank you for waiting.

52
00:05:39,883 --> 00:05:40,875
It's really late.

53
00:05:40,906 --> 00:05:41,820
Sorry.

54
00:06:05,875 --> 00:06:07,578
I get it.

55
00:06:09,633 --> 00:06:10,984
Please come home soon

56
00:06:11,555 --> 00:06:14,992
Wait, I have something to say.

57
00:06:15,533 --> 00:06:20,304
Don't forget any souvenirs

58
00:06:21,145 --> 00:06:27,343
Despite all my efforts to tighten your belt, the concert was unfortunately canceled.

59
00:06:28,580 --> 00:06:29,906
But I can't help it

60
00:06:29,930 --> 00:06:31,632
Due to work reasons,

61
00:06:33,195 --> 00:06:35,906
I think your sister at home is having a very hard time.

62
00:06:36,164 --> 00:06:37,609
Are you okay without being at home?

63
00:06:38,046 --> 00:06:39,775
She said she'd do everything herself

64
00:06:39,975 --> 00:06:41,640
She won't let me help her with anything.

65
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,406
That's so her.

66
00:06:44,836 --> 00:06:46,453
Be careful.

67
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:56,219
Nakan-chan.

68
00:06:57,218 --> 00:07:02,265
I have to go to Tokyo with the main family?

69
00:07:02,656 --> 00:07:03,398
You don't like?

70
00:07:03,556 --> 00:07:05,132
I don't want to go

71
00:07:05,867 --> 00:07:07,765
I can't get along with my brothers.

72
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:11,120
I feel like the water in Tokyo just doesn't seem to suit my tastes

73
00:07:11,556 --> 00:07:14,556
But if no one goes

74
00:07:14,867 --> 00:07:18,678
I think your sister feels lonely.

75
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:24,843
That's true, but if I end up being a nuisance to anyone,

76
00:07:25,014 --> 00:07:26,976
I want you to be a nuisance to you.

77
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,773
I'll also take care of Etsuko-chan

78
00:07:29,271 --> 00:07:31,707
Eventually, I will be able to earn money like Koi-san

79
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:33,966
So please.

80
00:07:33,990 --> 00:07:36,990
I would be grateful if Yukiko-chan could stay here

81
00:07:37,657 --> 00:07:39,390
Well then, please

82
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:45,070
But more importantly, why don't you take a blind date?

83
00:07:46,830 --> 00:07:51,171
There is a very good marriage proposal.

84
00:07:51,863 --> 00:07:53,226
about Jinba-san?

85
00:07:54,133 --> 00:07:55,570
You knew it.

86
00:07:57,630 --> 00:08:00,630
It's been four years since the first person I met had that happen

87
00:08:00,930 --> 00:08:02,584
And this is a good offer.

88
00:08:03,170 --> 00:08:05,488
You might like him.

89
00:08:06,178 --> 00:08:08,161
So please think about it

90
00:08:08,746 --> 00:08:11,746
but I know how Nakan-chan feels

91
00:08:12,695 --> 00:08:14,256
I'm really happy about it but...

92
00:08:15,031 --> 00:08:16,825
I know how you feel too.

93
00:08:17,446 --> 00:08:24,596
Yuko-chan, everyone really want you to find happiness as soon as possible

94
00:08:27,290 --> 00:08:29,632
I'm not telling you to forget about your past.

95
00:08:30,612 --> 00:08:33,006
so please give it some thought

96
00:08:33,764 --> 00:08:34,877
I will.

97
00:08:35,066 --> 00:08:35,659
Good.

98
00:08:36,758 --> 00:08:39,265
Anyway, I'm going to the main house now to check on your sister

99
00:08:39,818 --> 00:08:42,442
I've already made the kimono, so it's nice to see her

100
00:09:14,514 --> 00:09:15,668
Oh she's here.

101
00:09:15,848 --> 00:09:17,367
Hello

102
00:09:19,815 --> 00:09:22,241
you're bringing something so big.

103
00:09:22,621 --> 00:09:24,074
Let's go.

104
00:09:26,023 --> 00:09:27,363
Hold on.

105
00:09:32,198 --> 00:09:33,078
Welcome.

106
00:09:33,258 --> 00:09:34,218
Hello.

107
00:09:37,651 --> 00:09:38,591
Oh you are here.

108
00:09:38,636 --> 00:09:39,971
Hello.

109
00:09:40,861 --> 00:09:42,621
There're many stuff here.

110
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:46,158
You seems to be doing fine.

111
00:09:47,010 --> 00:09:49,588
I thought you'd be crying like crazy

112
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:53,305
Ah, I'm so tense while I'm doing this,

113
00:09:53,810 --> 00:09:56,546
but I think that once I get to Tokyo I'll relax and start crying

114
00:09:57,735 --> 00:09:59,187
This is Suzuri.

115
00:10:00,891 --> 00:10:03,095
I remember my dad making me buy this.

116
00:10:03,142 --> 00:10:03,948
Is that right?

117
00:10:04,420 --> 00:10:07,420
It cost hundreds of yen in those days

118
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:11,497
Because my dad loved expensive stuff.

119
00:10:11,581 --> 00:10:13,408
He was like that.

120
00:10:13,649 --> 00:10:15,409
So his Business was going badly.

121
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:18,884
He was complaint about the world.

122
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:20,997
Are you taking these to Tokyo?

123
00:10:21,166 --> 00:10:23,439
No, I'm thinking of selling them.

124
00:10:24,356 --> 00:10:25,043
Why?

125
00:10:25,274 --> 00:10:28,571
If I take such a luxury item, It doesn't fit into my life from now on.

126
00:10:28,705 --> 00:10:31,511
What a fool! This smells like my dad.

127
00:10:31,610 --> 00:10:35,348
It's ridiculous and the smell alone is not enough to make me eat

128
00:10:36,169 --> 00:10:38,562
Since you are decided to go to Tokyo, you have changed yourself.

129
00:10:39,076 --> 00:10:39,955
What do you mean?

130
00:10:40,075 --> 00:10:44,654
You've always said that hearts are precious.

131
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:49,940
I said that, but now it's important to eat,

132
00:10:50,692 --> 00:10:52,387
You might be right.

133
00:10:53,071 --> 00:10:54,967
This is my favorite.

134
00:10:55,329 --> 00:10:58,020
I'll give it to you, take good care of it.

135
00:10:59,497 --> 00:11:00,322
What else.

136
00:11:00,742 --> 00:11:02,700
I want something more.

137
00:11:02,896 --> 00:11:04,205
You're greedy.

138
00:11:07,212 --> 00:11:08,296
Here's album.

139
00:11:08,321 --> 00:11:10,476
Wow, a rare award came out

140
00:11:12,986 --> 00:11:16,295
Sister, Look, this is our mother. She was beautiful woman.

141
00:11:22,770 --> 00:11:24,785
This is Koi-san,right?

142
00:11:25,984 --> 00:11:26,838
Oh yeah.

143
00:11:27,403 --> 00:11:31,097
At this time, she was bothering everyone because she didn't want to be photographed

144
00:11:39,590 --> 00:11:40,832
There's Yoko-chan.

145
00:11:42,298 --> 00:11:43,788
I was when she graduated from school

146
00:11:44,152 --> 00:11:46,653
She looked nice too.

147
00:11:48,701 --> 00:11:51,556
I thought she would be the happiest.

148
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:57,980
was our dad smiling like this?

149
00:11:58,270 --> 00:12:00,546
I wonder what New Year's holiday it was

150
00:12:00,570 --> 00:12:02,077
When we first put it out in the store.

151
00:12:02,726 --> 00:12:04,659
It was really flashy.

152
00:12:05,715 --> 00:12:07,300
I can still see it now, sis

153
00:12:09,414 --> 00:12:10,105
Sis.

154
00:12:11,010 --> 00:12:14,010
I didn't imagine that Kyoka moved out of Osaka

155
00:12:16,875 --> 00:12:20,002
The rumor of destroying here and
building a new building is really, sister?

156
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:24,231
It's up to the person who bought it

157
00:12:26,143 --> 00:12:28,476
We could sold this house,

158
00:12:29,682 --> 00:12:32,537
We were able to pay off the debts our father had when he was in business,

159
00:12:32,945 --> 00:12:35,111
and we moved back home to Tokyo

160
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:36,839
That's true, but

161
00:12:38,652 --> 00:12:39,852
You know what.

162
00:12:41,315 --> 00:12:45,237
We must be strangers who have come to adopt.

163
00:12:46,390 --> 00:12:49,946
We went out of business because of it.

164
00:12:51,132 --> 00:12:56,028
I thought that studying to become a banker
was the way to protect the Makioka family

165
00:12:56,053 --> 00:12:57,331
Honestly, I don't think that much

166
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,855
I've heard that before but

167
00:13:00,186 --> 00:13:05,936
Then you should be more than happy for us to go to Tokyo.

168
00:13:07,390 --> 00:13:12,672
Yuko-chan and Koi thought I ruined this main house.

169
00:13:13,168 --> 00:13:15,436
You think too much.

170
00:13:17,090 --> 00:13:19,243
Sis, what's that? That's Yoko's kimono

171
00:13:22,377 --> 00:13:23,983
What a nice.

172
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:29,606
My dad did it for me that I just want to be able to get married anytime

173
00:13:30,905 --> 00:13:36,894
He was so unhappy man.
He was nice at first time.

174
00:13:37,841 --> 00:13:40,349
Yukiko-chan liked that person too

175
00:13:41,220 --> 00:13:43,117
We promised to go see a movie together and Yoko-chan is waiting for us

176
00:13:43,747 --> 00:13:48,236
On the way to the restaurant, his car crashed into track.

177
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,589
Human life is a fleeting thing.

178
00:13:51,650 --> 00:13:53,662
Don't talk about him anymore.

179
00:13:54,430 --> 00:13:56,026
But that was already four years ago

180
00:13:56,809 --> 00:14:00,032
I think Yukiko-chan's big emotional wounds are gradually healing

181
00:14:01,706 --> 00:14:02,579
And what more.

182
00:14:03,541 --> 00:14:04,159
What?

183
00:14:04,555 --> 00:14:07,555
Actually, Yoko-chan has a marriage proposal right now.

184
00:14:08,523 --> 00:14:09,596
Really?

185
00:14:10,041 --> 00:14:12,455
I'll look into it a bit more and let you know the details

186
00:14:13,250 --> 00:14:16,477
Yuko-chan, let me take care of this.

187
00:14:17,263 --> 00:14:20,263
But I feel sorry for Teinosuke.

188
00:14:20,293 --> 00:14:23,226
You don't have to worry about him.

189
00:14:23,718 --> 00:14:24,876
Yeah.

190
00:14:25,579 --> 00:14:27,685
but I'll ask to what our family says

191
00:14:31,191 --> 00:14:33,530
Dad is back.

192
00:14:33,947 --> 00:14:35,991
This place is very messy.

193
00:14:36,102 --> 00:14:38,351
Welcome back.

194
00:14:38,376 --> 00:14:39,410
Oh you are here.

195
00:14:43,294 --> 00:14:45,469
Don't play there.

196
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:48,759
The date for your trip to Tokyo has been decided?

197
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:52,143
I was forced something from main office.

198
00:14:53,324 --> 00:14:55,597
I won't be able to visit koi's exhibition.

199
00:14:55,939 --> 00:14:56,812
Sorry.

200
00:15:00,778 --> 00:15:04,166
Ah, I forgot about the souvenirs. Ah, leave them all here.

201
00:15:05,337 --> 00:15:06,470
The souvenirs are coming soon

202
00:15:09,083 --> 00:15:10,083
I wonder what's this.

203
00:15:10,119 --> 00:15:12,150
Sweets or toys?

204
00:15:12,892 --> 00:15:13,958
Open it.

205
00:15:15,609 --> 00:15:16,852
Here it is.

206
00:15:17,797 --> 00:15:18,931
Give it to me

207
00:15:45,952 --> 00:15:46,885
Koi?

208
00:15:47,362 --> 00:15:48,890
Oh, Mary.

209
00:15:49,314 --> 00:15:50,557
Congratulations.

210
00:15:51,660 --> 00:15:52,491
Thank you.

211
00:15:53,255 --> 00:15:57,252
This woman, Mary, works at an American trading company in Motomachi

212
00:15:57,749 --> 00:15:59,063
Her Japanese is very good.

213
00:15:59,530 --> 00:16:05,132
Everyone,I become Koi-san's student and become an artist.

214
00:16:05,469 --> 00:16:07,675
Thank you in advance.

215
00:16:07,741 --> 00:16:08,747
She speaks Kansai dialect.

216
00:16:08,795 --> 00:16:11,465
The person who taught her Japanese is from Osaka

217
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:12,248
That's right.

218
00:16:13,532 --> 00:16:16,619
She's Yamamura-style's Osho.

219
00:16:17,912 --> 00:16:18,809
The dancer?

220
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:20,640
Yeah.

221
00:16:21,087 --> 00:16:23,179
I wonder if I want to be your student

222
00:16:23,647 --> 00:16:24,804
Do you mind?

223
00:16:25,173 --> 00:16:26,464
OK OK

224
00:16:27,724 --> 00:16:29,299
You look fun.

225
00:16:31,061 --> 00:16:32,532
Please excuse me for a moment

226
00:16:33,882 --> 00:16:34,888
Thanks for your hard work.

227
00:16:35,244 --> 00:16:36,359
Let's go to Noda,Keibon.

228
00:16:36,810 --> 00:16:39,036
Are you going to make a pamphlet?

229
00:16:39,060 --> 00:16:42,000
Yes, I want one in front of the venue too

230
00:16:42,967 --> 00:16:45,142
You're working so hard.

231
00:16:45,969 --> 00:16:46,738
Good luck

232
00:16:47,325 --> 00:16:49,203
Go get the credit properly.

233
00:16:49,743 --> 00:16:50,858
Let me see.

234
00:16:54,275 --> 00:16:55,911
Is he Okahata's Keibon?

235
00:16:56,349 --> 00:16:58,830
He's a son of a jewelry store owner in Shinsaibashi.

236
00:16:59,330 --> 00:17:01,117
They used to run away together,

237
00:17:01,191 --> 00:17:02,106
Holding their hands?

238
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:03,825
Of course.

239
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:08,739
It was widely reported in the newspapers, and both houses were chased

240
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:20,160
Nakan chan's are coming soon.

241
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:23,454
I see. I have to go home soon

242
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,711
This is a celebrate the exhibition.

243
00:17:28,079 --> 00:17:29,236
Handbag?

244
00:17:29,670 --> 00:17:30,932
Open that handbag

245
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,496
There's a brooch inside

246
00:17:32,593 --> 00:17:34,648
That's so sweet.

247
00:17:34,673 --> 00:17:35,304
It costs a lot.

248
00:17:35,329 --> 00:17:36,090
I know

249
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:39,834
Thank you for your hard work.

250
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:52,405
Nakan-chan, He's Keibon

251
00:17:53,616 --> 00:17:54,531
Really?

252
00:17:56,582 --> 00:17:57,564
Welcome.

253
00:17:57,915 --> 00:17:59,412
Oh, I saw Jinba-san just now

254
00:17:59,541 --> 00:18:01,167
I made a promise here

255
00:18:01,846 --> 00:18:04,079
He's waiting for you at the cafe

256
00:18:05,220 --> 00:18:06,296
I'm going to go for a bit.

257
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:10,608
Let's play with dolls together.

258
00:18:14,810 --> 00:18:17,427
Hello, how is it going for a while?

259
00:18:17,817 --> 00:18:20,805
Have you looked into it yourself since then?

260
00:18:21,150 --> 00:18:24,262
Yes, he us the president of Kansai Electric Railway

261
00:18:24,950 --> 00:18:27,519
He has a good reputation at his workplace

262
00:18:27,644 --> 00:18:29,491
Everything was exactly as you told

263
00:18:29,586 --> 00:18:32,380
Isn't it time to go on a blind date?

264
00:18:32,642 --> 00:18:36,520
I did, but I had to ask permission from my home base

265
00:18:37,190 --> 00:18:38,983
I'm sorry to say this but

266
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:43,559
I feel sorry for Yukiko if the main family is being so strict

267
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,400
That's just as you say

268
00:18:46,475 --> 00:18:50,177
Anyway,they are urging you to hurry up

269
00:18:51,140 --> 00:18:54,140
The president of Kansai Electric Railway has been very helpful to us

270
00:18:54,863 --> 00:18:56,129
So please.

271
00:18:57,447 --> 00:18:58,254
I guess that's right

272
00:19:03,890 --> 00:19:07,387
Yeah yeah yeah yeah

273
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:10,692
