1102
01:20:08,876 --> 01:20:14,673
This is what I received when he put on your fur coat last winter

1103
01:20:15,320 --> 01:20:21,549
And this was when he was making something called Afternoon

1104
01:20:23,507 --> 01:20:29,252
In fact, he brought a lot of items from the store for you.

1105
01:20:30,250 --> 01:20:34,241
That being said, I am in no way betraying Koi-san

1106
01:20:35,170 --> 01:20:36,626
I feel bad.

1107
01:20:36,650 --> 01:20:39,976
He did a lot for Koi.

1108
01:20:41,250 --> 01:20:44,250
so please, please, please take care of it

1109
01:20:45,029 --> 01:20:46,945
I have to go.

1110
01:20:53,836 --> 01:20:54,851
Oharu.

1111
01:20:56,148 --> 01:20:57,898
Where's her?

1112
01:21:27,125 --> 01:21:27,914
Koi.

1113
01:21:29,085 --> 01:21:31,859
Have a drink.

1114
01:21:35,637 --> 01:21:37,890
Keibo's Baya just visited us.

1115
01:21:37,961 --> 01:21:39,929
Oharu told me.

1116
01:21:43,166 --> 01:21:46,944
I had a fight with Keibon and we broke up cleanly

1117
01:21:48,457 --> 01:21:51,686
If you're going to break up, then break up

1118
01:21:52,400 --> 01:21:55,400
You have to make amends.

1119
01:21:57,590 --> 01:21:58,726
it's not like that

1120
01:21:59,860 --> 01:22:02,860
He followed me around forever,

1121
01:22:03,880 --> 01:22:05,210
I was so annoying.

1122
01:22:06,050 --> 01:22:10,700
But Keibon have been causing a lot of financial trouble

1123
01:22:11,030 --> 01:22:14,030
That's ridiculous and it's definitely not true

1124
01:22:15,153 --> 01:22:16,128
Seriously?

1125
01:22:17,667 --> 01:22:20,249
I've been doing my own thing.

1126
01:22:20,930 --> 01:22:23,930
You know I was saving money too

1127
01:22:24,292 --> 01:22:26,897
People don't think that way.

1128
01:22:27,370 --> 01:22:29,756
There's no job for Keibon.

1129
01:22:31,623 --> 01:22:35,046
I was thinking that if I had to support Keibon, I would

1130
01:22:37,223 --> 01:22:38,484
Well, I'd like to ask

1131
01:22:39,025 --> 01:22:44,452
Wasn't the fur coat you got last winter made by KEIBON?

1132
01:22:45,273 --> 01:22:51,523
I was selling a rose-patterned haori and a kimono that fit into a vertical frame,and bought it.

1133
01:22:52,459 --> 01:22:56,101
but the old lady at Keibon said, "I paid for that."

1134
01:22:56,538 --> 01:22:58,800
She showed me the receipt.

1135
01:22:59,269 --> 01:23:02,905
That afternoon dress was like that too.

1136
01:23:03,323 --> 01:23:06,125
I don't want you to believe what she says.

1137
01:23:09,060 --> 01:23:11,866
I want to trust Uchika and Ko-san, but

1138
01:23:11,890 --> 01:23:14,242
The Baya has solid evidence

1139
01:23:15,395 --> 01:23:16,825
If that's the case, then

1140
01:23:16,850 --> 01:23:19,496
Well, how about you show me some real evidence?

1141
01:23:21,812 --> 01:23:28,317
She said she remembers the ring, the brooch, everything.

1142
01:23:29,582 --> 01:23:31,106
He was disowned

1143
01:23:31,545 --> 01:23:34,545
Apparently, she said he was the cause of the problem when he took out the jewels from the store

1144
01:23:34,830 --> 01:23:36,293
That's not fair

1145
01:23:36,614 --> 01:23:37,388
She said that.

1146
01:23:39,895 --> 01:23:41,067
Koi-san

1147
01:23:42,997 --> 01:23:45,340
The thing I want to say most about all of this is,

1148
01:23:45,365 --> 01:23:49,457
Why didn't you clearly break up with Keibon while you were dating Itakura-san?

1149
01:23:50,570 --> 01:23:54,489
People might think that you took money from KEIBON and supported ITAKURA.

1150
01:23:55,350 --> 01:23:57,035
That's something you do in night business.

1151
01:23:59,114 --> 01:24:00,785
You just used him

1152
01:24:01,530 --> 01:24:03,520
Now he is no longer be of any use.

1153
01:24:03,545 --> 01:24:05,739
You say such horrible things to him

1154
01:24:07,470 --> 01:24:10,470
why can't you reply?

1155
01:24:13,101 --> 01:24:17,973
I'm going to Tokyo again soon, but I'll just say this

1156
01:24:18,790 --> 01:24:23,707
Until now, I only wish your happiness.

1157
01:24:26,309 --> 01:24:31,528
It would be ridiculous to think that a
woman can find true happiness that way

1158
01:24:32,490 --> 01:24:35,036
You doesn't understand my feelings

1159
01:24:35,061 --> 01:24:35,888
Why?

1160
01:24:35,913 --> 01:24:37,403
You doesn't understand my feelings

1161
01:25:34,870 --> 01:25:36,832
The doctor will come soon

1162
01:25:41,117 --> 01:25:44,117
Yukiko says she won't return to Tokyo and will take care of you.

1163
01:25:45,068 --> 01:25:46,387
I'm sorry

1164
01:25:50,248 --> 01:25:52,613
I know about my health

1165
01:25:54,570 --> 01:25:57,950
Maybe three or four mouth.

1166
01:25:59,395 --> 01:26:00,981
Keibon's baby?

1167
01:26:04,833 --> 01:26:05,645
If so

1168
01:26:08,692 --> 01:26:09,832
Miyoshi's baby.

1169
01:26:11,110 --> 01:26:12,746
He is a bartender.

1170
01:26:13,153 --> 01:26:16,153
You're going to have his baby?

1171
01:26:17,630 --> 01:26:19,333
I want to have a baby if I can.

1172
01:26:39,179 --> 01:26:40,645
Take care of yourself.

1173
01:26:52,231 --> 01:26:55,496
Who will tell koi that she has an ectopic pregnancy?

1174
01:26:56,469 --> 01:26:58,684
